FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777295491
OL,3,CShelterbox photographer says disaster
OL,4,Cstories inspiring London Marathon
OL,5,Ceffort
OL,7,F"I wanted to challenge myself, and a
OL,8,Fmarathon distance for me is massive,
OL,9,Fbut also when the opportunity came up
OL,10,Fto run for Shelterbox, it was a no-
OL,11,Fbrainer because it's a charity that I
OL,12,Freally care about," Amy said.
OL,14,FThis will be Amy's first marathon
OL,15,Feffort - and she admits the training
OL,16,Fhas been tough going, particularly
OL,17,Fbattling through the harsh Cornish
OL,18,Fwinter.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777295491
OL,3,CShelterbox photographer says disaster
OL,4,Cstories inspiring London Marathon
OL,5,Ceffort
OL,7,F"The weather has been interesting at
OL,8,Fthe start of this year, it's been
OL,9,Fpretty full-on, but thankfully the
OL,10,Fspring is just about springing now so
OL,11,Fhopefully a bit more sunshine and dry
OL,12,Fdays ahead," she said.
OL,14,F"I'm a bit nervous, but I've had
OL,15,Ffriends and family who have run it in
OL,16,Fthe past and people have given me bits
OL,17,Fof advice.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
