CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777295491
OL,3,CShelterbox photographer says disaster
OL,4,Cstories inspiring London Marathon
OL,5,Ceffort
OL,7,F"People just keep telling me how much
OL,8,Ffun I'm going to have. People keep
OL,9,Fsaying 'The volume of what you're
OL,10,Fgoing to hear, people shouting and
OL,11,Fcheering is just unmatched.'
OL,13,F"So I'm definitely looking forward to
OL,14,Fthat atmosphere and just soaking it
OL,15,Fall up."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
