OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777295491
OL,3,CShelterbox photographer says disaster
OL,4,Cstories inspiring London Marathon
OL,5,Ceffort
OL,7,FAmy has worked as part of the content
OL,8,Fteam at Shelterbox for seven years,
OL,9,Foften travelling to disaster-hit parts
OL,10,Fof the world and capturing powerful
OL,11,Fimages to illustrate the charity's
OL,12,Fvital work.
OL,14,F"I've really been able to see how the
OL,15,Fright support at the right time can
OL,16,Fmake such a difference for families,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
