FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777295491
OL,3,CShelterbox photographer says disaster
OL,4,Cstories inspiring London Marathon
OL,5,Ceffort
OL,7,F"The last trip I went on was to
OL,8,FJamaica following Hurricane Melissa. I
OL,9,Fformed one of the first teams in, and
OL,10,Fto see that level of destruction was
OL,11,Freally quite shocking.
OL,13,F"There was one individual named
OL,14,FJennifer, she looked me right in the
OL,15,Feye and she said 'Our number one need
OL,16,Fright now is shelter.'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777295491
OL,3,CShelterbox photographer says disaster
OL,4,Cstories inspiring London Marathon
OL,5,Ceffort
OL,7,F"She was saying that as all of her
OL,8,Fhome was sort of strewn across the
OL,9,Ffloor. I know the impact of the work
OL,10,FShelterbox does, I've seen it first-
OL,11,Fhand, so it's definitely something
OL,12,Fthat's going to be driving me forward
OL,13,Fon the day."
OL,15,FAmy has already raised more than
OL,16,F#2,500 - she will be hoping for a few
OL,17,Fmore donations before she takes to the
OL,18,Fstart line on Sunday morning.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
